[
    {
        "Key": "page1.1",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "拿着铜钱，我和妮塔很快在基地里找到肴，没想到卜卜竟然也在这里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.2",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "早呀，分析员，妮塔。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.3",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "肴这是怎么了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.4",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她来找我占卜退休的时间，但我卜到一半，她就睡着了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.5",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那占卜的结果是什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.6",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "别提了，每次快有结果时就天雷大作，肴怕是要打一辈子工了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.7",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还好肴睡着了……不用听到这么可怕的事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.8",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "咦！我看你们两位红光满面，精神焕发，似乎是要遇到好事情了呢！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.9",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯？会有什么好事情？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.10",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看起来，这是一份机缘。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.11",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "鸡……圆？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.12",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "机——缘，就是机会和缘分。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.13",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有这种机缘的话，就不能靠简单的掐算，得拿出真本事来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.14",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说完，卜卜不知从哪里拿出了一个装满木签的竹筒出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.15",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "请吧！从这里面抽一支出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.16",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔来选吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.17",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我……我吗？但我一直运气都不太好……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.18",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没关系的，现在这可是承载了我们两个人的期冀。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.19",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果是这样的话，那我就有信心了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.20",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘿呀！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.21",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔闭上眼睛，凭直觉选了一支签。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.22",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "让我看看……哎！分析员，这上面写着上上签！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.23",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "的确，很不错呢，妮塔。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.24",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恭喜恭喜，另外，签上应该还有一些签文来着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.25",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "<orange>“巨石天降，不伤分毫”。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.26",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "<orange>“机关重重，亦无所惧”。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.27",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "<orange>“他山之石，可以攻玉”。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.28",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "<orange>“破局之法，且往东行”。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.29",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜天师，上面的字我都认识，但连起来什么都看不懂啊！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.30",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不急不急，让我想想。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.31",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "签的大致意思是，你们要找的东西在<orange>东边，有巨石和机关的地方 。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.32",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "至于他山之石，可以攻玉……唔，本天师一时间也不得解法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.33",
        "Speaker": "H妮塔",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我明白了，这句话的意思一定是……<orange>不管石头还是玉，都一拳打爆!</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.34",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（还真是简单又粗暴的理解……）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.35",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜，还有没有更具体一些的提示？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.36",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个……天机不可泄露，说得太多，机缘可就抓不住了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.37",
        "Speaker": "H卜卜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员这么厉害，一定能找到的！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.38",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……我尽力吧。",
        "disable": 0
    }
]